body_html: This is most likely due to double not being supported by ops by default on mobile TF. You can try converting your double ops to float, or building with selective registration/adding it manually to types.cc
body_text: This is most likely due to double not being supported by ops by default on mobile TF. You can try converting your double ops to float, or building with selective registration/adding it manually to types.cc
body: This is most likely due to double not being supported by ops by default on mobile TF. You can try converting your double ops to float, or building with selective registration/adding it manually to [types.cc](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/core/framework/types.cc#L240)
